<template>
    <v-network-graph
      class="graph"
      :nodes="nodes"
      :edges="edges"
    />
  </template>
  
  <script>
  import { VNetworkGraph } from 'v-network-graph'
  
  export default {
    components: {
      VNetworkGraph
    },
    data() {
      return {
        nodes: {
          node1: { name: "Node 1" },
          node2: { name: "Node 2" },
          node3: { name: "Node 3" },
          node4: { name: "Node 4" },
        },
        edges: {
          edge1: { source: "node1", target: "node2" },
          edge2: { source: "node2", target: "node3" },
          edge3: { source: "node3", target: "node4" },
        }
      }
    }
  }
  </script>
  
  <style>
  .graph {
    width: 800px;
    height: 600px;
    border: 1px solid #000;
  }
  </style>
